AiConfig.name: 文心一言
AiConfig.script: (function(){var e=document.querySelector('.yc-editor');if(!e){return console.error('Editable div not found');}e.focus();document.execCommand('insertText',false,'[message]');['keydown','keypress','input','keyup'].forEach(function(t){var n=new Event(t,{bubbles:true,cancelable:true});if(t==='keydown'||t==='keypress'||t==='keyup'){n.key='Enter';n.code='Enter';n.keyCode=13;}e.dispatchEvent(n);});setTimeout(function(){e.dispatchEvent(new KeyboardEvent('keydown',{key:'Enter',code:'Enter',keyCode:13,bubbles:true,cancelable:true}));},500);})();

AiConfig.name: Kimi Chat
AiConfig.script: (function(){const editor=document.querySelector('[data-testid="msh-chatinput-editor"]');const message='[message]';if(!editor){return console.error('Editor not found');}const insertText=(text)=>{const textEvent=new InputEvent('beforeinput',{data:text,bubbles:true,cancelable:true,inputType:'insertText'});editor.dispatchEvent(textEvent);};insertText(message);setTimeout(()=>{const enterEvent=new KeyboardEvent('keydown',{bubbles:true,cancelable:true,keyCode:13,key:'Enter',code:'Enter',shiftKey:false});editor.dispatchEvent(enterEvent);},500);})();
